== Spanish ==
=== Etymology ===
Latin ''[[minor]]''
=== Adjective ===
'''menor''' ''m'', ''f''
# [[smaller|Smaller]].  Comparative form of ''[[pequeño]]''
# [[younger|Younger]].  Comparative form of ''[[joven]]''
'''el menor''' ''m'', '''la menor''' ''f'', '''lo menor''' ''n''
# Superlative form of (1) and (2).  The [[smallest]], the [[youngest]].

